THE STATEMON VARIABLES TO CREATE

---- db.py
    val_mean_image_seen     # the mean number of times active images have been seen
    n_images_activated      # the number of images that have been activated so far
    n_workers_registered
---- mturk.py
    val_account_balance     # the current account balance
    n_hits_disabled
    n_hits_disposed
---- webserver.py
    n_tasks_generated
    n_practices_generated
    n_workers_banned
    n_workers_unbanned
    n_tasks_accepted
    n_tasks_rejected
    n_tasks_served          # includes practices and real tasks
    n_tasks_in_progress     # includes practices and real tasks
    n_practices_rejected
    n_practices_passed




